This little plasmoid provides a configuration interface and a switch to start/stop Redshift daemon.
See Redshift website for more detailed info <http://jonls.dk/redshift/>.

Known problem
Only one instance of this plasmoid can be executed, infact multiple instances will interfere
each others.

Developed by:
Diego Cristina <diegocc100 AT gmail DOT com>
Simone Gaiarin <simgunz AT gmail DOT com>

Code under GPLv3 license (see COPYING)

Requires:
KDE SC 4.x
Redshift

How to install:
plasmapkg -i redshift.plasmoid
